## Key Commands

### CPU Control

```bash
gt block <bead-id>              # Make task exclusive (blocks all other ready work)
bd dep add <A> <B>              # A depends on B (B must complete first)
bd dep add <A> <B> --type=blocks # A and B cannot run together
```

**When to use each:**

| Pattern | Command | Use Case |
|---------|---------|----------|
| Workflow formulas | `gt sling spec-workflow ...` | Default for all significant work |
| Dependency ordering | `bd dep add A B` | B must complete before A |
| Mutual exclusion | `bd dep add A B --type=blocks` | A and B both expensive, don't run together |
| One-off exclusive | `gt block <id>` | Single expensive task outside workflow |


