## Quality Gates

Before dispatching implementation, ensure quality gates pass:

### Beads Review (Built into beads-workflow)

Step 2 of `beads-workflow` runs 3-agent review:
- Forward: Every plan task has a matching bead
- Reverse: Every bead traces to the plan
- Dependencies: Graph integrity matches plan phasing

**Output:** `plans/{{ "{{" }}feature{{ "}}" }}/04-beads/beads-review.md`

### BV Robot Triage (Project-Level Only)

`spec-project-workflow` Step 9.5 runs bv robot triage:

```bash
bv --robot-quality --robot-by-label sfgastown
# All beads must score > 30
```

**Catches:**
- Missing descriptions
- Unlinked dependencies
- Wrong issue types
- Duplicate work

**Prevents:** Polecats running bad work → CPU waste

